<p begin="190190000t" end="245820000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle0">&#x202a;便利便利萬歲 便利便利萬歲&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;便利便利萬歲 人類&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="246910000t" end="306520000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle1">&#x202a;怒髮衝冠了嗎？怒髮衝冠了嗎？&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;怒髮衝冠了嗎？人類&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="307640000t" end="337330000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle2">&#x202a;WHAT&#x27;S UP不安因素超多&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;犯罪永遠不會消失&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="338330000t" end="366310000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle3">&#x202a;WHAT&#x27;S UP不安因素超多&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;(在怨念設下陷阱誰會掉落?)&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="367360000t" end="396030000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle4">&#x202a;WHAT&#x27;S UP不安因素超多&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;犯罪永遠不會消失&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="397060000t" end="417310000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle5">&#x202a;WHAT&#x27;S UP不安因素超多&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="430760000t" end="544760000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle6">&#x202a;HEY HEY!歌頌人類&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;逃避愛 人類不安嗎？&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="545870000t" end="634270000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle7">&#x202a;HEY HEY!人類支配人類&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;我們人類永遠有不安全感&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="635300000t" end="653610000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle8">&#x202a;嗚呼!人類…&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="658320000t" end="668560000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle9">&#x202a;WHAT&#x27;S UP,PEOPLE?!&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="678340000t" end="689260000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle10">&#x202a;WHAT&#x27;S UP,PEOPLE?!&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="697360000t" end="708280000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle11">&#x202a;WHAT&#x27;S UP,PEOPLE?!&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="716710000t" end="727630000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle12">&#x202a;WHAT&#x27;S UP,PEOPLE?!&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="742740000t" end="783700000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle13">&#x202a;偏見?陰險人類是糞便&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;開始行動的我Fight&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1594250000t" end="1619850000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle14">&#x202a;龍崎,怎麼了?&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1702030000t" end="1712950000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle15">&#x202a;怎麼了?&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1720380000t" end="1769750000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle16">&#x202a;第25話 沉默&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1814140000t" end="1858740000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle17">&#x202a;殺人筆記本的這一頁&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;角落被裁掉了一小張&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1859850000t" end="1889200000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle18">&#x202a;如果在那張紙片寫上人名&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;那個人也會死嗎&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1896220000t" end="1943890000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle19">&#x202a;我沒有這樣子用過&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;所以不曉得會怎麼樣&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1952610000t" end="1983210000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle20">&#x202a;那麼,死神只吃蘋果嗎?&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1984310000t" end="2000580000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle21">&#x202a;沒這回事&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2001660000t" end="2031580000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle22">&#x202a;但是死神的內臟也退化了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2032690000t" end="2069660000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle23">&#x202a;不,應該說進化了&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;所以不需要吃東西&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2082740000t" end="2092410000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle24">&#x202a;夜神&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2121450000t" end="2156720000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle25">&#x202a;好不容易才重獲自由&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;你卻幾乎都沒離開過總部&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2173830000t" end="2203750000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle26">&#x202a;海砂小姐來找你&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;你們也只是站著聊幾分鐘&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2211870000t" end="2242470000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle27">&#x202a;你們可以到外面自由地談憑愛啊&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2252580000t" end="2283520000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle28">&#x202a;KIRA事件還沒有解決&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2284610000t" end="2312250000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle29">&#x202a;我沒有談憑愛的心情&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2313310000t" end="2354610000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle30">&#x202a;還是說我一直待在總部&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;你覺得很礙眼呢&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2366690000t" end="2374990000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle31">&#x202a;不是&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2615270000t" end="2647920000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle32">&#x202a;現在我還不能去制裁罪犯&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2657320000t" end="2682920000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle33">&#x202a;海砂,就交給你來制裁了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2727050000t" end="2740020000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle34">&#x202a;海砂&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2741070000t" end="2762000000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle35">&#x202a;我們一起創造新的世界吧&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2988980000t" end="3072370000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle36">&#x202a;「最好小心點神在看著」&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3073400000t" end="3158730000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle37">&#x202a;「在黑暗的夜裡請牽著手」&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3159820000t" end="3200780000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle38">&#x202a;「就算我一個人在遠方」&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3201860000t" end="3265910000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle39">&#x202a;「你也隨時可以找到我」&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3266930000t" end="3343270000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle40">&#x202a;「把你知道的事情全部教我」&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3353350000t" end="3398630000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle41">&#x202a;「就算我不記得了」&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3399720000t" end="3493470000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle42">&#x202a;「不管幾次你都會教我」&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3531860000t" end="3655650000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle43">&#x202a;「但要是我全都會了」&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;「該怎辦呢?」&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3738730000t" end="3749310000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle44">&#x202a;這是怎麼回事&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3758750000t" end="3774330000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle45">&#x202a;又有罪犯被制裁了嗎?&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3779770000t" end="3800360000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle46">&#x202a;光是昨晚就有16人&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3801460000t" end="3826710000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle47">&#x202a;全都是火口死亡之後&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;才被報導出來的&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3827820000t" end="3846820000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle48">&#x202a;層出不窮耶&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3847840000t" end="3883790000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle49">&#x202a;KIRA果然不是火口嗎&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3884880000t" end="3932890000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle50">&#x202a;不,在我們逮捕火口之前&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;的確是他在制裁罪犯&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3933930000t" end="3965210000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle51">&#x202a;那就是出現了其他的KIRA嗎?&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3982310000t" end="3996300000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle52">&#x202a;怎麼會這樣&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3997320000t" end="4017000000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle53">&#x202a;可惡的KIRA&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4027020000t" end="4055690000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle54">&#x202a;這個KIRA…怎麼回事?&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4070390000t" end="4084720000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle55">&#x202a;怎麼會這樣?&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4095420000t" end="4110320000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle56">&#x202a;一定是海砂做的&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4119110000t" end="4145050000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle57">&#x202a;剛好發生在彌海砂獲得自由之後&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4146140000t" end="4170820000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle58">&#x202a;龍崎,你怎麼還提這個啊&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4171830000t" end="4192420000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle59">&#x202a;這件事和海砂無關吧&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4193520000t" end="4220820000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle60">&#x202a;要說的話&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;是剛好在火口死了之後吧&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4227220000t" end="4239160000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle61">&#x202a;這倒是沒錯&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4259580000t" end="4310550000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle62">&#x202a;既然有另一本筆記本&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;而且還有某個人在使用…&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4330320000t" end="4355570000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle63">&#x202a;那就一定要把他抓出來&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4419080000t" end="4444330000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle64">&#x202a;雖然死神說他不知道&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4451110000t" end="4491720000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle65">&#x202a;但是,假如用紙片也可以殺人&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4528190000t" end="4541840000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle66">&#x202a;那就有可能了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4550870000t" end="4588180000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle67">&#x202a;不過,曾在筆記本寫下名字的人&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4589250000t" end="4623830000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle68">&#x202a;若是沒有在13天之內&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;寫入下一個名字就會死&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4637960000t" end="4666630000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle69">&#x202a;而夜神月和彌海砂都還活著&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4677330000t" end="4707020000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle70">&#x202a;13天,問題就在這裡&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4727720000t" end="4774020000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle71">&#x202a;但是,龍崎&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;在筆記本寫名字的人被抓到以後&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4775100000t" end="4819700000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle72">&#x202a;真的可以用&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;連續殺人的罪名起訴定罪嗎&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4820810000t" end="4846410000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle73">&#x202a;這還需要問嗎?&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4847500000t" end="4887770000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle74">&#x202a;我們都知道有人死了&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;上面又寫了那些人的名字耶&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4888880000t" end="4930860000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle75">&#x202a;既然不能公開筆記本的存在&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;那就應該全部銷毀&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4940600000t" end="4962550000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle76">&#x202a;銷毀這種講法有點誇張&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4963620000t" end="4996270000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle77">&#x202a;不過&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;高層應該會採取類似的措施吧&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4997320000t" end="5027580000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle78">&#x202a;如果對方承認使用筆記本殺人&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;那就是死刑&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5028690000t" end="5047000000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle79">&#x202a;少說也是終生監禁&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5066720000t" end="5082300000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle80">&#x202a;沒錯吧&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5090080000t" end="5124090000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle81">&#x202a;你在想什麼,夜神月&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5125120000t" end="5150720000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle82">&#x202a;要是海砂被逮捕了,你自己…&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5172160000t" end="5213460000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle83">&#x202a;原來如此,這個傢伙真可怕&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5233560000t" end="5285210000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle84">&#x202a;夜神月非常篤定&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;我一定會拯救海砂的生命&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5290950000t" end="5314950000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle85">&#x202a;這種情況之下,為了救海砂&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5315970000t" end="5356930000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle86">&#x202a;只好由我&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;將龍崎的本名寫進我的筆記本&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5365020000t" end="5393350000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle87">&#x202a;而且我因為殺了龍崎&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5414070000t" end="5446380000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle88">&#x202a;既然關係到海砂的壽命&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5447440000t" end="5465750000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle89">&#x202a;所以我也會死…&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5466790000t" end="5507060000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle90">&#x202a;一切都會變得對夜神月最有利&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5537190000t" end="5553460000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle91">&#x202a;雷姆,你會怎麼做?&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5554540000t" end="5599820000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle92">&#x202a;你雖然是個死神&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;可是非常關心海砂&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5612270000t" end="5657550000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle93">&#x202a;你不會對&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;壽命又減短的海砂見死不救&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5663650000t" end="5685600000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle94">&#x202a;想想海砂的幸福吧&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="6297290000t" end="6322540000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle95">&#x202a;龍崎,你在那裡做什麼&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="6376370000t" end="6404010000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle96">&#x202a;我問你在那裡做什麼&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="6534520000t" end="6558180000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle97">&#x202a;龍崎,你在這裡做什麼&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="6559210000t" end="6591180000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle98">&#x202a;其實也沒什麼重要的事&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="6606600000t" end="6619570000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle99">&#x202a;只是鐘聲…&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="6627950000t" end="6638190000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle100">&#x202a;鐘聲?&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="6646640000t" end="6690670000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle101">&#x202a;是啊,今天的鐘聲感覺特別吵&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="6734390000t" end="6747360000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle102">&#x202a;我什麼都沒聽到啊&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="6756750000t" end="6768010000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle103">&#x202a;是這樣嗎?&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="6774760000t" end="6822770000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle104">&#x202a;今天的鐘聲一直沒停過&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;讓我根本沒辦法不理會&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="6833490000t" end="6875810000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle105">&#x202a;教會的鐘聲吧&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;有人結婚嗎?還是說…&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="6876870000t" end="6897800000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle106">&#x202a;你在說什麼?龍崎&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="6898890000t" end="6924830000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle107">&#x202a;別說那些無聊事了,我們進去吧&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="6940260000t" end="6952880000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle108">&#x202a;不好意思&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="6964290000t" end="6992960000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle109">&#x202a;我說的話&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;大家都會當成是胡扯&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="6993980000t" end="7013660000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle110">&#x202a;所以千萬不要相信&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="7104430000t" end="7118760000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle111">&#x202a;說的也是,龍崎&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="7126110000t" end="7155460000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle112">&#x202a;你說的話大部份都是胡扯的&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="7156480000t" end="7186740000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle113">&#x202a;如果每句話都要認真思考&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;那就沒完沒了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="7187840000t" end="7213090000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle114">&#x202a;這一點我是最清楚的&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="7232890000t" end="7254160000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle115">&#x202a;你說的沒錯,月&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="7275930000t" end="7310850000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle116">&#x202a;不過,這一點我們是彼此彼此吧&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="7329320000t" end="7340920000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle117">&#x202a;什麼意思&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="7361350000t" end="7410380000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle118">&#x202a;出生到現在,你曾說過真心話嗎&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="7474800000t" end="7498460000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle119">&#x202a;你在說什麼啊,龍崎&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="7499490000t" end="7522810000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle120">&#x202a;我的確偶爾會說謊&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="7529180000t" end="7585500000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle121">&#x202a;但是…&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;不會有人一輩子都沒說過謊吧&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="7595920000t" end="7627550000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle122">&#x202a;人類並非是那麼的完美&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="7628620000t" end="7649890000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle123">&#x202a;任何人都會說謊&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="7650970000t" end="7711610000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle124">&#x202a;但是我一直小心&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;不說會傷人的謊話&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="7712700000t" end="7726350000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle125">&#x202a;這就是我的回答&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="7764750000t" end="7782720000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle126">&#x202a;我就知道你會這麼說&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="7827480000t" end="7855460000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle127">&#x202a;我們進去吧,全身都濕了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="7866850000t" end="7875150000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle128">&#x202a;好&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="7999320000t" end="8017290000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle129">&#x202a;還真是狼狽呢&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="8018340000t" end="8050990000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle130">&#x202a;都是你害的吧&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;誰叫你待在那種大雨之中&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="8057380000t" end="8082980000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle131">&#x202a;說的也是,對不起&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="8165820000t" end="8182430000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle132">&#x202a;龍崎,你在做什麼&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="8183500000t" end="8225820000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle133">&#x202a;看你這麼認真的在擦身體&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;我想幫你的忙&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="8226880000t" end="8249860000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle134">&#x202a;不用了,你不需要這麼做&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="8250900000t" end="8270810000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle135">&#x202a;還可以幫你按摩喔&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="8271930000t" end="8294230000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle136">&#x202a;算是為了贖罪&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="8295280000t" end="8318260000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle137">&#x202a;我可是很會按摩的&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="8332650000t" end="8354950000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle138">&#x202a;隨便你吧&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;好&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="8436090000t" end="8460430000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle139">&#x202a;喂&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;很快就會適應的啦&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="8560880000t" end="8574190000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle140">&#x202a;又弄濕了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="8610260000t" end="8620500000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle141">&#x202a;對不起&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="8851500000t" end="8863780000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle142">&#x202a;感覺真寂寞&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="8904560000t" end="8921850000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle143">&#x202a;我們馬上就要分開了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="9003320000t" end="9012300000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle144">&#x202a;喂&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="9040030000t" end="9059030000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle145">&#x202a;我知道了,我馬上過去&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="9104090000t" end="9128770000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle146">&#x202a;月,我們走吧&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="9129780000t" end="9152080000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle147">&#x202a;看來似乎進行得順利&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="9260910000t" end="9286510000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle148">&#x202a;龍崎,這是怎麼回事&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="9287610000t" end="9327200000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle149">&#x202a;竟然有國家&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;同意將筆記本用來執行死刑&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="9328310000t" end="9352990000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle150">&#x202a;渡,你做得很好&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="9354010000t" end="9362310000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle151">&#x202a;過獎了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="9363350000t" end="9406350000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle152">&#x202a;請你快點準備將筆記本送過去吧&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="9407390000t" end="9418650000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle153">&#x202a;好的&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="9419740000t" end="9438740000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle154">&#x202a;龍崎,這是怎麼回事&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="9449440000t" end="9475040000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle155">&#x202a;驗證殺人筆記本的效力&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="9499490000t" end="9548180000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle156">&#x202a;你現在這麼做又有什麼意義&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;這筆記本明顯就是有效的啊&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="9549200000t" end="9572520000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle157">&#x202a;而且要由誰來寫上名字呢&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="9573560000t" end="9630900000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle158">&#x202a;只要一開始寫&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;13天期限的事就會沒完沒了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="9631950000t" end="9691560000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle159">&#x202a;可以找一個即將在&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;13天之內執刑的死刑犯來寫&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="9692680000t" end="9746040000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle160">&#x202a;如果他寫完後過13天還沒死&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;就免除他的死刑&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="9756070000t" end="9793380000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle161">&#x202a;但是這樣簡直把人命當兒戲&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;就只差一點了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="9794450000t" end="9832790000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle162">&#x202a;只要能突破這一點&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;一切都全部串聯起來了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="9883540000t" end="9901850000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle163">&#x202a;怎麼了,停電嗎&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="10016000000t" end="10024980000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle164">&#x202a;渡?&#x202c;</p>
